<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8445711312764361136">Tim Ferriss is author of three #1 NYT/WSJ bestsellers: <i>The 4-Hour Workweek</i>, <i>The 4-Hour Body,</i> and <i>The 4-Hour Chef.</i> He is also a start-up advisor specializing in positioning, PR, and marketing (Uber, Evernote, etc.). When not damaging his body with abusive sports, he enjoys chocolate, bear claws, and Japanese animation.<br/> </span>

